        "value": "SeaMo is a season-aware multimodal foundation model for remote sensing that integrates spatial, multimodal, and multi-seasonal information using a masked image modeling framework. It employs unaligned spatial region selection, multi-source inputs, and temporal-multimodal fusion blocks to explicitly model spatial, spectral, and seasonal dimensions, enhancing generalization and robustness across geoscientific tasks.",
